  "ui_gameOver_shareText": "🚀 STELLAR BROADCAST\n\nI didn't survive... {reason}.\nThink you can do better on the same voyage?\nstellarbroadcast://play?seed={seedCode}\n\nDon't have the app?\nhttps://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.quickapps.stellar_broadcast",
